## MultiStageTimer.stop() method

Stops the `MultiStageTimer`<!-- -->. Returns the measurement of the last stage, which may be `undefined` if not all stages started.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
stop(): number;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

number
